  "title": "CLASS 3 DRIVER",
  "description": "<p>6 days’ work week</p><p>Island-wide delivery</p><p>Able to commit to work on weekends & public holidays<br /></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Collect soiled laundry from customers and deliver clean laundry to hotels on time;</li><li>Plan and follow an efficient delivery route to maximize time and fuel usage while meeting customer deadlines;</li><li>Provide friendly and professional customer service when picking up or delivering laundry, addressing any questions or concerns;</li><li>Maintain accurate records of deliveries and pickups, including customer information, special instructions, and completed tasks;</li><li>Regularly inspect the delivery vehicle, ensuring it is clean, fueled, and well-maintained;</li><li>Report any mechanical issues or required repairs to supervisors.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Singapore LTA-issued Class 4 Driving License;</li><li>Work on weekends and public holidays;</li><li>Physically fit;</li><li>Strong customer service and communication skills;</li><li>Organizational skills for handling orders, paperwork and delivery schedules;</li><li>Safety Awareness;</li><li>Ability to work independently and manage time effectively;</li><li>Valid LTA-issued driver’s license;</li><li>Possesses a clean driving record.</li></ul>",
