    "description": "<p>For over 50 years, California Laundry is proud to deliver premium quality linen and laundry services tailored to the intricate demands of the hospitality industry. Here, we understand that every piece of impeccable laundry creates a lasting impression on your guests, and we are committed to delivering exceptional standards of quality. We offer a complete range of intelligent laundry solutions and professional linen management backed by meticulous staff and systems that cater to your specialised requirements. We are fully committed to your success and creating the right, desired impressions for your guests that are undoubtedly the top priority in hospitality.</p>",
